Package gameClient

Class NodeData

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameClient.NodeData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    node_data
    public class NodeData
extends java.lang.Object
implements node_data
    This class represent a Vertex object on a graph which implemented by given node_data api. Contains functions that define a vertex on a directed weighted graph such as: setLocation and setWeight (which isn't used)
